   "source": [
    "# 🎟️ Coupon Classifier & Ranker\n",
    "\n",
    "## Problem Statement\n",
    "Coupon platforms show offers like:\n",
    "- **Flat Rs.150 cashback** → guaranteed value\n",
    "- **Upto Rs.500 cashback** → uncertain, usually much lower actual value\n",
    "\n",
    "A user cannot easily compare these two. This project builds an ML model that:\n",
    "1. **Classifies** the coupon type (Flat Cashback, Upto Cashback, Flat %, Upto %)\n",
    "2. **Predicts** the real expected value of each coupon\n",
    "3. **Ranks** coupons so the user always picks the best one\n",
    "\n",
    "## Input & Output\n",
    "| Input | Output |\n",
    "|-------|--------|\n",
    "| Raw coupon text | Coupon type + Expected ₹ value + Rank |\n",
    "\n",
    "## Why is this both Classification & Regression?\n",
    "- **Classification** → What type is this coupon?\n",
    "- **Regression** → What is the real expected cashback amount?"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "b4911a74-3334-47cf-bbe1-9358710d5fea",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
