    "- UPTO_CASHBACK → 25 samples\n",
    "- FLAT_PERCENT → 25 samples\n",
    "- UPTO_PERCENT → 25 samples\n",
    "\n",
    "## Future Scope\n",
    "- Scrape GrabOn, CouponDunia, CashKaro using Selenium\n",
    "- Add real redemption data to improve regressor"
