    "# 6. Model Training & Evaluation\n",
    "\n",
    "## Two models:\n",
    "- **Classifier** → predicts coupon type (FLAT_CASHBACK, UPTO_CASHBACK, FLAT_PERCENT, UPTO_PERCENT)\n",
    "- **Regressor** → predicts expected real cashback value in Rs."
